T02D3456:112a-1: dharma dh'a tu b'a g'i shva ra s'a dha nam ba shya bi dhi:/
T02D3456:112a-3: chos kyi dbyings ngag gi dbang phyug gis grub thabs
T02D3456:112a-4: dbang du bya ba'i cho ga /'phags pa 'jam dpal
T02D3456:112b-0: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas 'dir stong @112b pa
T02D3456:112b-1: nyid du bsgoms pa'i rjes la padma dang zla ba
T02D3456:112b-2: la gnas pa'i ho:yig dmar po yongs su gyur pa
T02D3456:112b-3: las phyag brgyad pa zhal bzhi pa /
T02D3456:112b-5: g-yas kyi gur gum ltar dmar ba /
T02D3456:112b-6: rgyab kyi padma r'a ga ltar dmar ba /
T02D3456:112b-8: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis kyis gzhu dang /
T02D3456:112b-10: phyi ma dag gis zhags pa dang /
T02D3456:112b-12: yang phyi ma dag gis shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i po ti dang /
T02D3456:112b-14: de bzhin du phyi ma dag gis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa'o //
T02D3456:112b-15: chags pa chen pos sgeg pa'i nyams 'bar ba /
T02D3456:112b-16: sna tshogs padma dang zla ba la rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
T02D3456:112b-18: rgyan dang 'od pag tu med pa dang /
T02D3456:112b-19: ral pa'i cod pan gyis brgyan pa /
T02D3456:112b-20: snying ga'i sa bon gyi 'od zer gyis sems can
T02D3456:112b-21: rnams bkug nas rang dbang med pa'i gnas la bkod
T02D3456:112b-23: aom ma h'a r'a ga badzra r'a ga ya sarba satva na ho /
